<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1294809>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A: Arboraptor viridis sp. nov., head, frontal view; B: Odontophlugis sp., head frontal view; C: Anisophlugis appendiculata (Gorochov, 2012), head and thorax lateral view; D: Phlugis sp., head and prothorax, lateral view; E: Cephalophlugis cephalotes (Bolívar, 1888) (adapted from Gorochov, 1998), terminalia, lateral view; F: Arboraptor viridis sp. nov., terminalia dorsal view; G: Odontophlugis pehlkei (Kästner, 1932) (adapted from Gorochov, 1998), terminalia lateral view; H: Neophlugis calabaza Gorochov, 2012 (adapted from Gorochov, 2012), terminalia dorsal view; I: Phlugiola longipeles Mendes et al. 2017, terminalia dorsal view; J: Paraphlugiola helenae Cadena-Castañeda et al. 2014, terminalia dorsal view; K: Tyrannoraptor arboreus nov. comb., terminalia dorsal view; L: Phlugis teres (De Geer, 1773), terminalia lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1294809/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

